        "MISSING: renewal_retry_attempts_total (counter, labels: attempt_number) — tracks retry volume and distribution. Required for the 24-hour retry SLO.",
        "MISSING: renewal_retry_exhausted_total (counter) — renewals that exhausted all retries. Each one is lost revenue with no alert.",
        "MISSING: renewals_pending_retry (gauge) — current retry queue depth.",
        "MISSING: renewal_duplicate_total (counter) — detects idempotency failures that could double-charge customers."
