      {
        "scenario": "Billing API responds but slowly (latency degradation)",
        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "No timeout alert. billing_api_duration_seconds is collected but has no alert on p99 latency. Slow responses cause backpressure, growing the queue silently until the 1-hour SLO is breached. Add alert on p99 > threshold and implement request timeouts."
