        "scenario": "Retry mechanism fails or stalls",
        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "No retry metrics exist. If retries silently stop, failed renewals are permanently lost. Add retry queue depth metric, retry attempt counter, and alert on retry_exhausted events."
      },
      {
        "scenario": "Queue backlog grows faster than processing capacity",
        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "No queue depth metric. Cannot detect capacity saturation until renewals breach the 1-hour SLO window. Add queue depth gauge with alert on sustained growth."
